Package RiskApplication.RisksServer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    This class contains code for the start up of the Jetty server which contains my jersey web service framework as a servlet.
    AppTest
    Unit test for simple App.
    AuthenticationFilter
    This class contains code for validating tokens provided by the Google Sign-In for websites framework.
    DBConnection
    This class contains code for all communication between Jersey and the database.
    InviteEmail
    This class contains code sending emails to users using SMTP2GO
    Project
    This class is used for the temporary storage of projects converted from JSON.
    Risk
    This class is used for the temporary storage of risk events converted from JSON.
    RiskServer
    This class contains code for defining the routing of URLs to java functions.
    Slack
    This class contains all functionality for interaction with the slack API.
